<head>
  <link href="sign_up.scss" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="contentwrap">
      <div class="ppage-header">
	     <p class="hheader">회원가입</p>
      </div>
      <hr class="linee">
       <div class="form-horizontal offset-3">
              <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                <%= devise_error_messages! %>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="inputEmail" class="col-sm-2 control-label" style="text-align: left;">이메일</label>
                  <div class="col-sm-8">
                  <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "form-control" , placeholder: "likelion@likelion"%>
                  <p class="help-block mt-3 mb-1">입력한 이메일로 인증메일이 발송됩니다.</p>
                  <p class="help-block">반드시 사용중인 이메일주소를 입력해주세요. 비밀번호 분실 시 이메일을 통해 재설정이 가능합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="inputName" class="col-sm-2 control-label" style="text-align: left;">이름</label>
                  <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <%= f. text_field :name, autofocus: true, class: "form-control", placeholder: "이름을 입력해주세요" %>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="inputPassword" class="col-sm-6 control-label" style="text-align: left;">비밀번호</label>
                  <div class="col-sm-8">
                      <% if @minimum_password_length %>
                      <% end %>
                      <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "비밀번호 6자리 이상", class: "form-control", placeholder: "6자리 이상" %>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="inputPasswordCheck" class="col-sm-6 control-label" style="text-align: left;">비밀번호 확인</label>
                  <div class="col-sm-8">
                    <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off",class: "form-control", placeholder: "비밀번호 확인"  %>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                     <label for="inputName" class="col-sm-2 control-label"></label>
                       <div class="col-sm-8">
                         <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">회원가입</button>
                       </div>
                </div>
              <% end%>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
